summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 29727, entitled: "An ordinance appropriating the sum of $579.75 from the light fund and $1.25 from the M.L. Extension Series "G" Fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of paying C. E. Gilmer, as foreman of Outside Construction, Lighting Department, back salary, and authorizing the drawing of a warrant therefor", approved July 24, 1912.
